refraction.book.misc.inv.content1=You might be wondering if there's a way to extract and insert items to and from inventories using light. Well... There is! The disperse (magenta) and attract (cyan) effects can insert and extract items to and from inventories respectively.
refraction.book.misc.inv.content2=The actual process however, is a bit crude... You see... You have to kinda... Burn a hole into the inventory with a burn beam first.  A laser pointing at the inventory will then extract or insert the items through that hole. So you must point a burn beam on the inventory desired.
refraction.book.misc.inv.content3=Physics is beautiful, isn't it?


